node.text: Lil recap of our @austinstreetbrewery collab release party at @thirstyportland 💛 Big thanks to all who came out. Make sure to head to Austin Street’s Fox St. location today for both versions on draft + mixed 4-packs of both in cans (from noon until sell out)!

node.text:
BBK snapped and corned some beautiful pastrami, so we’ve got a bangin’ Reuben going today!
-also, our ramp supply is dwindling down to the pickled bulbs, so our ramp dip has been replaced by a delicious Maine crab & pimento cheese option (includes those pickled bulbs!) 
-on tap and out of the bottle, we’ve got tons of ways to stay cool today. Kitchen till 7, bar/retail till 9.
🥵🧊🍺😎

node.text: Long before the brewery, @peterjensenbissell and @noahbissell were responsible for a daily paper route in their hometown (and current home of @bbbthreerivers) Milo, Maine. This grisette pays homage to that beautiful simplicity of a well-trodden loop: many grains, many strains, even more months, and a single foeder deliver a layered acidity and a vibrantly refreshing profile. Like pulling newspapers out of a sack at 5am every morning, it can be as intricate or as sleepy an experience as the day needs it to be. Available today 📰

node.text: Preserve & Protect is our tribute to @jensen.bissell 's 30 years of work in Baxter State Park - here are some words from the man himself 🌲 As always, 3% of sales from this double IPA are donated to Friends of @baxterpark , an independent citizen group with a mission to preserve, support, and enhance the character of this beautiful wilderness area. Available now in cans and pouring on draft!

node.text: Introducing A Long Dusk raspberry ale, the most fruited offering out of @bbbthreerivers so far. Heavily dosed with a TON of Maine raspberries (5 pounds per gallon) on a mixed-fermentation base aged in PX sherry casks, adding some extra warmth and character to the final balance. It took over 20 months for us to bring you this beer that spotlights one of our state's sweetest agricultural treasures. Enjoy a bottle today in our taproom or bring one home – either way, take your time and savor every single summery sip of this incredible raspberry-bomb-in-a-glass.

node.text: This week we’re bringing you cans of Preserve & Protect, Reciprocal, and Baby G alongside two brand new bottles from @bbbthreerivers 🍾🍾 Stay tuned for more on everything you see here!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 08, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
We’ve got two of our absolute bedrock beers available in cans today, twin pillars representing everything we work towards day in and day out! 
7 taps and plenty of new hitters on the menu (barbacoa tacos, @goransonfarm salad and the ribeye cheesesteak are all good places to start) will make for a lovely Sunday. Bar 11am, kitchen 12pm, both through 5.

node.text:
Our ribeye cheesesteak on @solocucinamarket semolina is back on special all weekend, because you love it, and we love you. This sandwich + a tall Precept…..not sure we need to elaborate much here 🤤 
Bar & can sales from 11, kitchen from 12.
